reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Quality cable. Does the job.
reviews.reviewText: These are quality USB 2.0 cables. I have it hooked up from my Yamaha 10XGU hardware mixer into my computer and the cable works perfectly. The gauge of the cable is heavy duty and not flimsy. The connectors are supposed to be gold plated, but the two I received looked like the plating was faded so more yellowish than gold. However, that did not hinder the performance of the cables in any way. I'm happy with the packaging, the product and the overall quality of these cables.
